{"tid":949411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國脅持　加拿大外交官　有匈牙利國籍　歐盟介入　局勢升級","createTime":"2018-12-20T19:02:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T21:11:18.000Z","uid":47714,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"6fbd9a7792922f93a392d919b609817fded34d40","tid":949411,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T19:02:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/康明凱另有匈牙利國籍-匈領事欲探訪未獲准-歐盟介入事件/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E5%BA%B7%E6%98%8E%E5%87%B1%E5%8F%A6%E6%9C%89%E5%8C%88%E7%89%99%E5%88%A9%E5%9C%8B%E7%B1%8D-%E5%8C%88%E9%A0%98%E4%BA%8B%E6%AC%B2%E6%8E%A2%E8%A8%AA%E6%9C%AA%E7%8D%B2%E5%87%86-%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F%E4%BB%8B%E5%85%A5%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%2F&d=0YVBAqgRK1L8n%2BFuuCtTf8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=5c71eccd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E5%BA%B7%E6%98%8E%E5%87%B1%E5%8F%A6%E6%9C%89%E5%8C%88%E7%89%99%E5%88%A9%E5%9C%8B%E7%B1%8D-%E5%8C%88%E9%A0%98%E4%BA%8B%E6%AC%B2%E6%8E%A2%E8%A8%AA%E6%9C%AA%E7%8D%B2%E5%87%86-%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F%E4%BB%8B%E5%85%A5%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%2F&h=c762b366\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/康明凱另有匈牙利國籍-匈領事欲探訪未獲准-歐盟介入事件/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://archive.is/2e41c/78f8752ad67d1bd6d5d6a264a709edba21714f82.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.is%2F2e41c%2F78f8752ad67d1bd6d5d6a264a709edba21714f82.png&h=2f7229bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國際危機組織高級顧問、前加拿大外交官康明凱（Michael Kovrig）在中國遭到拘留，外界普遍認為事件與加拿大應美國應求拘留華為CFO孟晚舟有關。路透社引述消息報道，康明凱，同時擁有匈牙利國籍，匈牙利駐北京大使館尋求探訪康明凱，暫未獲准許，由於匈牙利是歐盟成員，有消息人士指歐盟已介入事件。<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述數名消息人士表示，康明凱同時具有匈牙利國籍，會令歐盟捲入事件。有消息人士稱，匈牙利駐北京大使館正尋求探訪康明凱，但一直未獲批。另一消息人士指出，匈牙利駐北京大使館將此視為領事案件，正在走「正常程序」，但尚未獲得領事探訪批准。<br />\n<br />\n報道提到，康明凱年輕時正居於布達佩斯，參與搖滾樂隊，並在當地教授英語。<br />\n<br />\n由於擁有匈牙利國籍，康明凱也具有歐盟公民身份。報道指出，一名消息人士表示，歐盟已經直接向中國外交部提出關於康明凱的問題，也與加拿大駐北京大使保持聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士指出，加拿大外交部長方慧蘭（Chrystia Freeland）、以及歐盟外交及安全政策高級代表莫蓋里尼（Federica Mogherini），未來幾天可能會通電話討論康明凱案件。"},{"pid":"812fd6f6079520a538d3150fe4df5b827125d309","tid":949411,"uid":7790,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T19:04:43.000Z","msg":"又唔制裁中國，你班廢柴有撚用？<br />\n<br />\n學下Trump Trump<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"768e5827d431b84b0638a6e177df943a0decf28b","tid":949411,"uid":28195,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T19:04:48.000Z","msg":"中共今次佢自已都估唔到，捉蟲入屎忽喇"},{"pid":"b0119482ca8819e5be560bb06e78c08289982b9a","tid":949411,"uid":9394,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T19:05:18.000Z","msg":"又歐盟又加那大真好<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8bb4dded4022ab5d074c46b357daeae19b579aa","tid":949411,"uid":9681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T19:06:21.000Z","msg":"NATO <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nWW3 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b110dcc01c3434e333a5ba311e46e9c25cf5ff9","tid":949411,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T19:06:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce053909d3801002b17bc735fc1e45a51052a848","tid":949411,"uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T19:07:10.000Z","msg":"歐盟無咩料到"},{"pid":"d2f2ddb4bc806b3cc1b09e3411bc477c1dc4690a","tid":949411,"uid":76216,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T19:07:13.000Z","msg":"清朝義和團?"},{"pid":"3fcb67bd25e79ba332c01bba81222d6ded7e7cd